title: 309 Signature Tanks
description:
MATERIAL: 93% Cotton 7% Elastane.

FIT: Fitted.

DESIGN: A tank that reflects your gains in the gym. The signature tanks are designed to give you more coverage than a stringer but less than a tank. The back is a racerback cut perfect to display the upper back and deltoids. The fabric composition makes this tank super soft and stretchy at the same time.

MODEL: The model in the first photo is wearing a size Medium. Weight 180lb Height 5'9.
